Interface AvailabilitySet.DefinitionStages.WithCreate

    public static interface AvailabilitySet.DefinitionStages.WithCreate
extends Creatable<AvailabilitySet>, Resource.DefinitionWithTags<AvailabilitySet.DefinitionStages.WithCreate>, AvailabilitySet.DefinitionStages.WithUpdateDomainCount, AvailabilitySet.DefinitionStages.WithFaultDomainCount
    The stage of an availability set definition which contains all the minimum required inputs for the resource to be created (via Creatable.create()), but also allows for any other optional settings to be specified.
